{"tid":1545590,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣新聞：有「香港PTT」之稱的連登討論區串爆韓國瑜","createTime":"2019-09-06T03:31:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T09:44:40.000Z","uid":144372,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ecc3a43b9d808e45cac807478ef562930719919f","tid":1545590,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=597932\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D597932&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=27f05aa9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D597932&h=c1ec1de0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=597932</a><br />\n<br />\n國民黨總統參選人、高雄市長韓國瑜的國政顧問團總召張善政近日提出，考慮制訂「擴大香港學生來台就學管道，並放寬優秀香港學生畢業後在台就業限制」相關政策；結果消息傳到香港，引發當地網友熱烈討論，紛紛留言嗆韓國瑜，「你當選誰想過去？」<br />\n<br />\n對於香港「反送中」情勢變化，總統蔡英文日前赴國安會聽取香港狀況簡報，會後，蔡英文提出四點指示，除呼籲中國勿以台灣等他國關心作為指控外力介入的藉口，同時強調基於人道考量，對於在台港人，我們也會提供必要的協助，不會坐視。<br />\n<br />\n對此，張善政先是嘲諷蔡英文「指示內容了無新意」，還說自己將在國政顧問團中提議制訂「擴大香港學生來台就學管道，並放寬優秀香港學生畢業後在台就業限制」相關政策，並表示香港人來台念書其實沒有語文與生活的適應問題，文化背景也類似，期待可以與本國學生相處融洽。<br />\n<br />\n張善政這番發言相關半導，被轉發到了有「香港PTT」之稱的連登討論區（LIHKG），許多香港網友不以為意，更怒嗆「你當選就是下一個中國，過去有什麼用？」、「放寬香港人居留就業，因為香港是中國一部份」、「你當選就變台灣特別行政區，當然放寬」、「你當選誰想過去？」、「別相信！當選台灣就等於第二個香港，可能比香港還更不堪！」。"},{"pid":"1ad3519bc154878f9c6f0798923abdceff0f4072","tid":1545590,"uid":76702,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:31:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f644b87afd14d54e55eb62e95d6623c645b80b8a","tid":1545590,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d2b1174981047b48113864f2ddebe2a6d37e0a6","tid":1545590,"uid":266362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:32:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還我 831 真相！不要港版 64！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n［還我 831 真相］點解口吐白沫？原因在此！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1544189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1544189</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">大個仔</span>獨立必睇</span></span></span></strong><br />\n［召喚攬炒巴] 星球級反擊！香港最後本錢 VS 赤獸<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://lih.kg/1529054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1529054</a></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9 大核彈<span style=\"font-size: small;\">內容包括</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">：</span></span></span><br />\n(1) 基本法自古以來是中國領土的謬誤<br />\n(2) 中英聯合聲明的謬誤<br />\n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a9d6d90888e1230da3b1b3740466bedb5edb4969","tid":1545590,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:32:11.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H4MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=520cea27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"6deffab06be3c6c7b26a7bc14a4200015336c36f","tid":1545590,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:32:58.000Z","msg":"又消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33de975fbac4efc951b545e16f83836a26068add","tid":1545590,"uid":43322,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"兩地廢青connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606fa78bd5b5c28d8a015b86745cef6ee80b28d4","tid":1545590,"uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"33de975fbac4efc951b545e16f83836a26068add","tid":1545590,"uid":43322,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:34:43.000Z","msg":"兩地廢青connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"你咩事"},{"pid":"c704b89dbd99644d0e3ea9064de238797c3153dc","tid":1545590,"uid":